* fix(docs/graph/lca.md): 修改欧拉序列的代码

欧拉序列的`dfs`函数代码原为

```cpp
void dfs(int t, int depth) {
  dfn[++dfntot] = t;
  pos[t] = dfntot;
  dep[dfntot] = depth;
  for (int i = head[t]; i; i = side[i].next) {
    dfs(side[i].to, t, depth + 1);//here is a bug
    dfn[++dfntot] = t;
    dep[dfntot] = depth;
  }
}
```
但`dfs`只有两个参数，所以此`commit`删去了多余的那一个

